# 🧠 ELI5 Hub - Explain Like I'm Five

A beautiful web app that explains complex topics like you're 5 years old. No jargon, no shame.

## ✨ Features
- Simple, child-friendly explanations
- Works offline with mock explanations
- Optional AI backend (OpenAI) for real answers
- Copy explanations to clipboard
- Popular examples to get started

## 🚀 Quick Start (Frontend only)
Just open `index.html` in your browser! Works immediately with mock explanations.

## 🐍 Run with Backend (Real AI)
1. Get an OpenAI API key from https://platform.openai.com
2. Set environment variable: `export OPENAI_API_KEY='your-key-here'`
3. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
4. Run server: `python backend.py`
5. Open `index.html` - it will auto-connect to backend

